---
title: Sweet-Soy Crumbed Chicken & Sesame Pumpkin with Ponzu Slaw & Mayonnaise
description: We’re going to share a secret with you - it’s easy to elevate chicken just simply season with the flavours of sweet and soy in the
golden crumb. You can do the same with roast pumpkin by sprinkling over sesame seeds. A little change goes a long way.
